column5: Thanks to Terry I was able to use a work around to access the site and log in  Thanks Terry!!!  It's been a while and I guess I have a bit of catching up to do.  To start I made it out to the 10th annual Fishing for Tyler and as usual OFC'rs outdid themselves with their support and generosity!!!  Great to seem some of you and chat for a bit, I think I ended up with either sunburn or windburn, or a bit of both   All worth it though.  Maureen
You under stood what he was saying? I was at WHAT is he  dribbling about. LOL  Nice to see ya back Mo.
Nice to see you again Mo, I posted some pics, there is a great one of you
glad I was able to help and you got on   that's why they pay me the big bucks....lol
Great to see you back on the board Mo!
Do you mean I don't have to relay mesages for you no more...Thanks Terry...You da man !!!
Moe, It was really nice to see you again and I knew one of our "super techs" would be able to help you with your internet problem. Glad to see you vocal again!

Moe, It was really nice to see you again and I knew one of our "super techs" would be able to help you with your internet problem. Glad to see you vocal again! Never knew you left Happy to learn you all had a good event Saturday-nice pics--nice winning fish @ Ty's gig
Maureen good to see you get some help I hope all is well

Maureen good to see you get some help I hope all is well Oh, Moe needs lots more help than just getting back on line (did I say that out loud?) LOL.  Just kidding, Moe is one of my favorite people, heart of gold that gal!
Good to have you back Mo, I was wondering where you got to.
Welcome back Maureen. How are the kids?
Gidday again Mo!  Stick around eh!
Thanks guys, Roy, the "kids" are doing well, keeping me busy for sure.  Cliff, some would say I'm beyond help  Maureen
Welcome back Maureen glad to see you got the bug worked out.   Art
Cliff, some would say I'm beyond help  Maureen Hmmm...now, I wonder who would say a thing like that ???
